metadata.name: Transfer Station 1
metadata.description:
Each piece in Transfer Station is comprised of electronic waste sourced from local recyclers or donated directly from manufacturers, digitized using photogrammetry and arranged into a unique sculpture. Before we melt them down, let's take one more good look at them

Featured:
Canon R5, (Water damage)
Fluke Ti SBP3 (Internal fault)
Daytron DT505 (Corrosion)

1600x2000pix
400 Frames

Richard Parry, 2022
